âœ… Using Hex (Most Common)
Yes â€” Avalonia fully supports hex codes.

Standard 6-digit RGB:
<Window Background="#000000"/>
Format:

#RRGGBB
Example:

#FF0000 â†’ Red
#00FF00 â†’ Green
#0000FF â†’ Blue
âœ… With Alpha (Transparency)
You can also use 8-digit hex:

<Window Background="#FF000000"/>
Format:

#AARRGGBB
Where:

AA = Alpha

RR = Red

GG = Green

BB = Blue

Examples:

#FF000000 â†’ Solid black
#80000000 â†’ 50% transparent black
#00000000 â†’ Fully transparent
âœ… Using RGB Function Syntax
