        <SolidColorBrush Color="rgb(0,0,0)"/>
    </Window.Background>
</Window>
âœ… Using ARGB Function Syntax
<SolidColorBrush Color="rgba(0,0,0,1)"/>
Where:

Last value = opacity (0 to 1)

âœ… Best Practice (Recommended Way)
