Changing text color in Avalonia UI is done via the Foreground property of text controls (TextBlock, Button, etc.). You can use:

Named colors (Red, Black, White)

Hex (#RRGGBB or #AARRGGBB)

Brushes in XAML resources

âœ… Example 1 â€” Simple Named Color
